ful product and process development coedited with hk bowen c holloway and sc wheelwright oxford university press  and revolutionizing product development with sc wheelwright the free press  a comprehensive study on product development in the world auto industry with t fujimoto product development performance was published in  by hbs press other books include dynamic manufacturing with rh hayes and sc wheelwright free press  and industrial renaissance with wj abernathy and am kantrow basic books  additional publications include managing in an age of modularity with cy baldwin harvard business review septemberoctober development projects the engine of renewal with hk bowen ca holloway and sc wheelwright harvard business review septemberoctober  organizing and leading heavyweight development teams with sc wheelwright california management review spring  capabilities and capital investment new perspectives on capital budgeting with cy baldwin journal of applied corporate finance  and the power of product integrity with t fujimoto harvard business review novemberdecember print entire profileless books book   dynamic manufacturing creating the learning organization robert h hayes steven c wheelwright and kim b clark citationhayes robert h steven c wheelwright and kim b clark dynamic manufacturing creating the learning organization new york ny free press  view details citeview detailsfind at harvard related book   design rules volume  the power of modularity carliss y baldwin and kim b clark keywords design governing rules regulations and reforms citationbaldwin carliss y and kim b clark design rules volume  the power of modularity cambridge ma mit press  chinese mandarin ed view details citeview details related book   design rules volume  the power of modularity carliss y baldwin and kim b clark keywords design segmentation citationbaldwin carliss y and kim b clark design rules volume  the power of modularity cambridge ma mit press  view details citeview detailsfind at ha