pointed him president of byu–idaho on january   it was announced that effective april   clark would be succeeded by clark gilbert as the president of byu–idaho lds church service and familyedit clark has served in various assignments in the lds church including bishop scoutmaster elders quorum president sunday school teacher and counselor in a stake mission presidency from  to  clark served as an area seventy in the churchs idaho area on april   clark was sustained as a member of the first quorum of the seventy on august   he succeeded paul v johnson as the commissioner of church education clark and his wife sue have seven children awardsedit eagle scout award by the boy scouts of america distinguished eagle scout award by the national eagle scout association newcomenharvard award for best paper published in the business history review  see alsoedit list of general authorities of the church of jesus christ of latterday saints chronological listing of church commissioners of education referencesedit  httpwwwdeseretnewscomarticlefivenewgeneralauthoritiessustainedduringldschurchsgeneralconferencehtmlpgall  a b prescott marianne holman august   seminary and institute histories to be released church news   a b c faculty  research faculty hbsedu harvard business school retrieved   contribution ignored help  heaps julie dockstader october   president installed at byuidaho lds church news retrieved    a b inauguration byuiedu byu idaho retrieved   contribution ignored help  mower daniel october   news releases byuiedu byu idaho archived from the original on   contribution ignored help  clark gilbert announced as new president of byui ksl january    new general authorities young men presidency and primary presidency changes announced newsroom retrieved  april    a b distinguished eagle scout award pdf marketing  communication division boy scouts of america  retrieved   further readingedit halter jon c september  achievements and challenges scouting  contribution ignored help